revision.text: ==English== ===Proper noun=== {{en-proper noun|Yambaos}} # {{surname|en}}. ===Statistics=== * According to the 2010 United States Census, ''Yambao'' is the 30367<sup>th</sup> most common surname in the United States, belonging to 770 individuals.
